Package ist.healthcheck.beans

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Call
    this class contains call historical data information relative to specific interval.
    GeneralConfiguration
    this class contains general information about Database server IP, Database server port Number, ICON database name, SpeechMiner database name, GIM database name, option to enable mail sender, option to enable SMS sender, database username, database password and account name.
    Interval
    this class contains historical data information about calls in a specific interval
    IntervalsWithDate
    this class encapsulate intervals historical data according to a specific time interval.
    MailConfiguration
    this class contains information about mail configuration needed information sender email, sender password , receivers, icons KPIs, speechminer KPIs, send mail if only the KPIs below average
    Pair<F,S>  
    SMSConfiguration
    this class contains information about SMS configuration needed information service URL, token, method, sender password, receivers, icons KPIs, speechminer KPIs, send mail if only the KPIs below average
